  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da7 \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dde\u0dbb\u0dc0 \u0daf\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0da2\u0db4\u0db1\u0dca \u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The President will go to Japan to pay his last respects to his friend",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe is going to Japan at the end of this month to attend the funeral ceremony of the former Prime Minister of Japan, Mr. Shinsho Abe.",
        "The former Prime Minister of Japan is a long-term political friend of President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "According to political sources, Mr. Shinsho Abe supported the development of Sri Lanka as the Prime Minister of Japan when Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe was the Prime Minister.",
        "While addressing a political meeting, Mr. Shinsho Abe passed away after being shot by a terrorist on July 8th.",
        "The funeral of Mr. Shinsho Abe is scheduled to be done in Japan on the 27th."
      ],
